==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unrealize
<hw>Un*re"al*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>realize</ets>.]</ety> <def>To make unreal; to
idealize.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His fancy . . . <qex>unrealizes</qex> everything at a touch.</q>
<rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unreally</ent>⟦br⟧
